Change History

Revision Date Notes
2.0.0 2019-07-17 Added DynamicSession2 service to indicate the following actions now require authentication:
  • GetDynamicSessions
  • GetDynamicSessionInfo

Services

DynamicSession

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/DynamicSession
This service provides creating and managing sessions on the router.

Service Actions

  • GetDynamicSessionInfo
  • GetDynamicSessions
  • ResetDynamicSession
  • StartDynamicSession
  • StopDynamicSession

DynamicSession2

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/DynamicSession2
This service provides creating and managing sessions on the router.

Service Actions

  • GetDynamicSessionInfo
  • GetDynamicSessions
  • ResetDynamicSession
  • StartDynamicSession
  • StopDynamicSession

Actions

GetDynamicSessionInfo

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/GetDynamicSessionInfo

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
sessionUUID UUID no Session UUID identifies the session.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
sessionInfo DynamicSessionInfo no Dynamic session information.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/GetDynamicSessionInfoResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorDynamicSessionDoesNotExist The dynamic session does not exist.
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/GetDynamicSessionInfo"

{
  "sessionUUID": "7e04d3bb-8789-4d6b-b8d1-d9b070dfe24e"
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "sessionInfo": {
      "sessionUUID": "7e04d3bb-8789-4d6b-b8d1-d9b070dfe24e",
      "remainingSessionTimeoutSeconds": 1200,
      "rules": [
        {
          "ruleUUID": "1d0a3262-3cdf-42e5-a9b0-1481f790055f",
          "ruleType": "DynamicPortRangeForwardingRule"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}

GetDynamicSessions

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/GetDynamicSessions
This action gets all the dynamic sessions on the router.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
sessionUUIDs UUID[] no An array of session UUIDs on the router.
maxDynamicSessions int no Max number of dynamic sessions allowed.
maxDynamicSessionTimeoutSeconds int no Max dynamic session timeout seconds allowed on the router.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/GetDynamicSessionsResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/GetDynamicSessions"

{
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "sessionUUIDs": [
      "c23de4d6-15d0-40bf-8f43-5d354b222992"
    ],
    "maxDynamicSessions": 20,
    "maxDynamicSessionTimeoutSeconds": 1200
  }
}

ResetDynamicSession

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/ResetDynamicSession
This action resets timeout value of a dynamic session.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
sessionUUID UUID no Session UUID identifies the session.
requestedDynamicSessionTimeoutSeconds int no Timeout Seconds of a dynamic session requested by caller.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
remainingDynamicSessionTimeoutSeconds int no Remaining timeout seconds of this dynamic session.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/ResetDynamicSessionResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorDynamicSessionDoesNotExist The dynamic session does not exist.
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/ResetDynamicSession"

{
  "sessionUUID": "7e04d3bb-8789-4d6b-b8d1-d9b070dfe24e",
  "requestedDynamicSessionTimeoutSeconds": 1200
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "remainingDynamicSessionTimeoutSeconds": 1200
  }
}

StartDynamicSession

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/StartDynamicSession
This action starts a new dynamic session.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
requestedSessionTimeoutSeconds int no Timeout Seconds requested by caller.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
sessionUUID UUID no Session UUID identifies the dynamic session.
remainingSessionTimeoutSeconds int no Remaining session timeout second of this dynamic session.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/StartDynamicSessionResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorRequestedTimeOutTooLong Max timeout seconds allowed on the router is 1200.
ErrorTooManyDynamicSessions Max number of sessions on the router is 20.
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/StartDynamicSession"

{
  "requestedSessionTimeoutSeconds": 600
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "sessionUUID": "7e04d3bb-8789-4d6b-b8d1-d9b070dfe24e",
    "remainingSessionTimeoutSeconds": 1200
  }
}

Structures

DynamicSessionInfo

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/DynamicSessionInfo
DynamicSessionInfo describes a dynamic session which has a session UUID, remaining session timeout seconds and rules associated with it.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
sessionUUID UUID no Session UUID identifies a dynamic session.
remainingSessionTimeoutSeconds int no Remaining timeout second of this session
rules RuleInfo[] no An array of rules assocated with a session

RuleInfo

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/RuleInfo
RuleInfo describes a rule associated with a dynamic session.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
ruleUUID UUID no Rule UUID identifies a rule.
ruleType RuleType no Rule type of the rule

Enumerations

RuleType

http://linksys.com/jnap/dynamicsession/RuleType
Rule type.

Enumeration Values

Value Description
DynamicSinglePortForwardingRule Dynamic single-port forwarding rule.
DynamicPortRangeForwardingRule Dynamic port range forwarding rule.
DynamicIPv6ConnectionRule Dynamic IPv6 connection rule.
HttpProxyRule Http proxy rule.
